  "title": "Environmental Control Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>ENVIRONMENTAL CONTROL OFFICER</strong></p>\n<p><strong>(ECO)</strong></p>\n<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensure all construction works are complied to Environmental Pollution Control and Public Health Acts &amp; Code of Practices</li>\n  <li>Ensuring the project Environmental Management Control Plans and system are complied with</li>\n  <li>Taking charge of all site Environment, Health and Hygiene matters</li>\n  <li>All matters on site in relation to the duties &amp; responsibilities of an ECO</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Certificate of Registration by NEA (ECO &amp; EMCO etc)</li>\n  <li>Candidate must possess at least a Professional Certificate / NITEC, Diploma or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Relevant years of experience in construction field such as HDB, D&amp;B projects etc</li>\n</ul>",
